  "description": "A bustling harbor scene featuring several boats and dock infrastructure. A long, grey metal gangway extends from the land towards a white boat, and then further to a vividly colored red and white fishing vessel with a tall mast. Multiple other boats of varying sizes and colors are visible in the background, alongside industrial structures like cranes and sheds. The water is calm with subtle ripples, reflecting the structures and boats, and the sky is bright blue with few clouds. The gangway is supported by weathered wooden pilings, adding a rustic touch to the otherwise industrial landscape.",
